  "body": "<p>Anytime I receive new products to play with, I get excited and can't wait to dive in. The double-sided adhesive sheet kit from Silhouette was no exception. I opened up Silhouette Studio and laid out a few designs onto the sheet. Because I prefer to cut a bunch of designs while the Silhouette SD is out, I may not actually have a particular project in mind.</p>\n\n\n\n\n\n\n<figure>\n\n\n<img src=\"https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0981/5667/5392/files/a723978daed6f8fe.png?v=1782537192\"/>\n\n\n<figcaption>\n<p><a href=\"http://www.designerdigitals.com/digital-scrapbooking/supplies/product_info.php/products_id/14242\">Ali Edwards Hello Heart 3X4 boxes</a> || camera || hearts</p>\n</figcaption>\n</figure>\n\n\n\n<figure>\n\n\n<img src=\"https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0981/5667/5392/files/0e4245301937f8ac.jpg?v=1782537195\"/>\n\n\n<figcaption>\n<p>After realizing I cut these initial shapes, I decided I would actually add some designs from the Digi shop at Studio Calico.</p>\n</figcaption>\n</figure>\n\n\n\n<figure>\n\n\n<img src=\"https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0981/5667/5392/files/4106ab8a446b5dc1.jpg?v=1782537198\"/>\n\n\n<figcaption>\n<p>The glitter and flocking set comes with a brush in the kit.</p>\n</figcaption>\n</figure>\n\n\n\n<figure>\n\n\n<img src=\"https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0981/5667/5392/files/c5113d1729f86582.jpg?v=1782537200\"/>\n\n\n<figcaption>\n<p>I peeled off the yellow backing and then stuck the shape down onto the front of the card. Then I peeled the white backing up, revealing the sticky residue. Then I poured the glitter on.</p>\n</figcaption>\n</figure>\n\n\n\n<figure>\n\n\n<img src=\"https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0981/5667/5392/files/ee0f0e7f8f2c7eb4.jpg?v=1782537203\"/>\n\n\n</figure>\n\n\n\n<figure>\n\n\n<img src=\"https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0981/5667/5392/files/2cc66a9363191315.jpg?v=1782537206\"/>\n\n\n<figcaption>\n<p>I work on a folded scratch piece of paper so that I can easily our the remaining glitter/embossing powder back into the container.</p>\n</figcaption>\n</figure>\n\n\n\n\n\n<img alt=\"5g-DSC_1413-600x398.jpg\" src=\"https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0981/5667/5392/files/136a2275860bb74b.jpg?v=1782537209\">\n</img>\n\n<img alt=\"5h-DSC_1414-600x398.jpg\" src=\"https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0981/5667/5392/files/c8e97d62a87949c6.jpg?v=1782537211\">\n</img>\n\n<img alt=\"5i-DSC_1415-398x600.jpg\" src=\"https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0981/5667/5392/files/d0ae2b8f207a6f95.jpg?v=1782537214\">\n</img>\n\n<img alt=\"5j-DSC_1416-600x398.jpg\" src=\"https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0981/5667/5392/files/e41583286278d683.jpg?v=1782537217\">\n</img>\n\n\n\n<p>Next I wanted to try using the embossing powders onto Project Life sized journaling cards for future spreads.</p>\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n<img alt=\"5k-DSC_1417-600x398.jpg\" src=\"https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0981/5667/5392/files/c40c06b49e909742.jpg?v=1782537220\"/>\n\n\n<img alt=\"5l-DSC_1418-600x398.jpg\" src=\"https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0981/5667/5392/files/90b7c60c9749838b.jpg?v=1782537222\"/>\n\n\n<img alt=\"5m-DSC_1421-600x398.jpg\" src=\"https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0981/5667/5392/files/94fb9c4f5f0d3482.jpg?v=1782537225\"/>\n\n\n\n\n<p>Really digging the way these turned out.</p>\n\n\n\n\n\n\n<figure>\n\n\n<img src=\"https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0981/5667/5392/files/8b0df2b469c6e7fe.jpg?v=1782537228\"/>\n\n\n</figure>\n\n\n\n<figure>\n\n\n<img src=\"https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0981/5667/5392/files/c63ab9cad8dc2b8f.jpg?v=1782537230\"/>\n\n\n</figure>\n\n\n<p>To take advantage of these great promotions:</p><ul><li><p>Visit <a href=\"http://www.silhouetteamerica.com/valentine/\">Silhouette</a> and use the promo code: TANGERINE through February 14th to get 1 Silhouette Portrait™ and 1 double-sided adhesive starter kit for $179.99.</p></li></ul><ul><li><p>For those who already have a cutting tool and are just interested in the double-sided adhesive starter kit, visit <a href=\"http://www.silhouetteamerica.com/valentine/\">Silhouette</a> and use promo code: TANGERINE to purchase for $12.99.</p></li></ul><p>Hope you enjoyed seeing a bit of the process and check out the <a href=\"http://www.silhouetteamerica.com/valentine/\">Silhouette Valentine Discounts</a>, valid using TANGERINE through February 14.</p>"
